headline: General Mills (NYSE:GIS) Announces Leadership Changes With Liz Mascolo Promoted To Segment President
summary: General Mills (NYSE:GIS) recently announced the retirement of Jon Nudi and the promotion of Liz Mascolo, marking significant leadership transitions. Over the past week, the company's shares rose 3%, while broader market conditions showed a decline, with the S&P 500 dropping 0.9% and the Dow Jones falling 0.2%.
